{"id":"443f8a2b9b1b562e15056142e2f60f58c8fd05ec45060215b70587cfe305ebab","item_id":"c474fe0672:0","text":"此节点提供一种现代方式来生成并分层 bump maps（凹凸贴图），用 shading（着色）而不是建模来添加细小表面细节，成本较低。"}
{"id":"22949313c601c551a048648c5f05f31e58ce634a32c97a77d57b247fb7ea6873","item_id":"c474fe0672:1","text":"传统选项不允许 order-independent mixing（与顺序无关的混合），而此节点可在需要时轻松混合多个输入。你也可以把这些节点串接起来，构建更复杂的网络，通过 masking（遮罩）在表面上改变 bump maps，同时只使用一个 material assignment（材质指定）。"}
{"id":"ee3e0440b5975e521c29c9ab4d4b8fe30146c38ddc687a1f3671364465a70836","item_id":"c474fe0672:2","text":"提供"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:3","text":"resultNG"}
{"id":"d9b5a20b920b9c4df67fbf0c23ab93b49eb8e44822fe0ab73d84121bb93bf2a7","item_id":"c474fe0672:4","text":"输出的节点可以连接到此节点，例如"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:5","text":"PxrTexture"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:6","text":"和"}
{"id":"4482b14d9497c6420781998c5b7b4cdd9ab83d18f11a48c4fb6b026b15526fdc","item_id":"c474fe0672:7","text":"许多 procedural patterns（程序化图案）"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:8","text":"。"}
{"id":"21b8113a3476cf5ccde1633bfb8ba7457ffc30c0a67db576403e3383ec9e2fbb","item_id":"c474fe0672:9","text":"这种新的 NG vector type 表达 signal 的 gradient（梯度），比传统 bump map 技术计算起来更准确、更高效。"}
{"id":"3b245a1dc5d7be4eec5441bed43ac3c883768298735b6252da1701251f440864","item_id":"c474fe0672:10","text":"此技术实现了以下论文中的许多发展："}
{"id":"bef5642b7eea51d0112fbe0c8869fb3377d0ed8d2143f94ef5e844917b1b0460","item_id":"c474fe0672:11","text":"Surface Gradient-Based Bump Mapping Framework"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:12","text":"。"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:13","text":"Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id":"5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff","item_id":"c474fe0672:14","text":"Mode（模式）"}
{"id":"9fd728c66c9a256b121472dabf32a34317aed01d8427d70ec830289cf23a7cc8","item_id":"c474fe0672:15","text":"Add（相加）"}
{"id":"11794f5f79d7609e456902862470a85ed24b2e5efb9fc0d2a69eaf6ccab03ca7","item_id":"c474fe0672:16","text":"- 将结果相加，A + B"}
{"item_id":"c474fe0672:17","text":"Over（叠加）"}
{"id":"b5f32c1da45e0b619fde428d4f39527f7f247cfbe7ba5cd5d6d7cee9a3b04484","item_id":"c474fe0672:18","text":"- 将 A 置于 B 之上；mask（遮罩）在这里很有用，可用来显露下方图层，A+B(1-a)"}
{"id":"63df016f961c5684d4c795008031fd4d9483e23dc827fe95dc385c782038b22b","item_id":"c474fe0672:19","text":"Subtract（减去）"}
{"id":"2480a1037288bfa092e1ad229213e9eebae9e43e1ed6aacea52f05b5474f0133","item_id":"c474fe0672:20","text":"- Subtract（减去）结果，A - B"}
{"id":"4c50b387f5157287995aad20e9a1e004ee6278d2628d4d96788bf8b97eb7a899","item_id":"c474fe0672:21","text":"Surface Gradient（表面梯度）"}
{"id":"d3f23ee67c2d5e75ebd8c8b8289cca9bb3895fd29dab46fe5184a7f75f5224e3","item_id":"c474fe0672:22","text":"将你的 pattern 或 texture 节点的"}
{"id":"51ea7c2272acaed16c436843571ecd0e652bafa3eb2b50b5ca18cde4597048f7","item_id":"c474fe0672:23","text":"resultNG"}
{"id":"e4edd0b532069042645b0fda443fa074c563c2f2f65209c9f939a5e01ac28ab0","item_id":"c474fe0672:24","text":"连接到此处。"}
{"id":"e368929abd3614e92ad17e56175b67d1f6ba94aca92ab43b7f16f31764ff7447","item_id":"c474fe0672:25","text":"Mask（遮罩）"}
{"id":"347ef6beb254d23bc6b743c89a09ad8ec49cb524b1684e3576294b7570ba5836","item_id":"c474fe0672:26","text":"一个简单的 grayscale（灰阶，scalar 标量）pattern 或 texture channel（纹理通道）会用于遮罩你希望此特定图层生效的位置。使用 Over 模式时，这尤其有用。"}
{"id":"49e96d7cdf58069cc793555324e2226642f2f7f8bfff4cebe0c11a61eecef60a","item_id":"c474fe0672:27","text":"Amount（强度）"}
{"id":"e485266ac254472f6be9806dd4c9df8095d55b7a60308c45da4ab6c52907b212","item_id":"c474fe0672:28","text":"这表示你希望此图层的 bump effect（凹凸效果）有多强，可使用 pattern 或 texture channel 等 scalar input（标量输入）进行控制。"}
{"id":"9f088dbebd6c3c70a5ddbc2c943b11e4ca9acea5757b0b4f2b32479f0dbb747e","item_id":"c474fe0672:29","text":"Advanced（高级）"}
{"id":"22e51f047f90beac7936ab4aca9ca2269e04e5ca5be52b8d38f9abf5a0c348d3","item_id":"c474fe0672:30","text":"Adjust Amount（调整量）"}
{"id":"cd9a6a17027769bd4753210951760eb685697a53a5e37dec9f99b94549909499","item_id":"c474fe0672:31","text":"有时你可能会在表面上看到变暗现象，可能出现在 horizon（地平线/掠射边界）处，此时 normal（法线）可能背向摄像机。此控制项可以把这些法线推回朝向摄像机，以避免这种 artifact（伪影）。"}
{"id":"18ee1ea9b251b0a841885c123ba86d48505ac30953edd385a239068d48aa9faa","item_id":"c474fe0672:32","text":"Surface Normal Mix（表面法线混合）"}
{"id":"0e2b5d2ba91599ca4214315854c69dc9cd3b6b3a32bce58e4e51c8bc5643f8d3","item_id":"c474fe0672:33","text":"此节点提供的 shading normals（着色法线）可以覆盖你的 surface geometry normals（表面几何法线）；如果你希望把这些 surface normals（表面法线）混入其中，可以使用此控制项。"}
